title: Driving Tips from Austin Cabot
description: Our guest is driving instructor Austin Cabot. He's led the instruction at Speed Venture and Gridlife track events, owned some awesome cars, and just bought...an ambulance. We talk about cars, how to drive fast, how to mod your car, and that ambulance.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
